<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Delete Your Account - IMPROVISE</title>

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: #f4f6f8;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.7;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }

    h1 {
      color: #111827;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h2 {
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #1f2937;
    }

    p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    ol, ul {
      margin-left: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .email-box {
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 6px;
    }

    .email-box strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    a {
      color: #2563eb;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        padding: 25px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container">
    <h1>Delete Your Account - IMPROVISE</h1>

    <p>
      You do not need to log into the app to request account deletion.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you would like to delete your account and associated data from IMPROVISE,
      please follow the steps below.
    </p>

    <div class="email-box">
      <strong>Email:</strong>
      <a href="mailto:support.improvise@gmail.com">support.improvise@gmail.com</a>

      <strong style="margin-top:10px;">Subject:</strong>
      Account Deletion Request
    </div>

    <h2>How to Request Account Deletion</h2>

    <ol>
      <li>Send an email to <strong>support.improvise@gmail.com</strong>.</li>
      <li>Use the subject line: <strong>"Account Deletion Request"</strong>.</li>
      <li>Include the email address associated with your account.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>What Will Be Deleted</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Your account information (Google account ID and email address).</li>
      <li>App usage data.</li>
      <li>Progress and other in-app data.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What May Be Retained</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Transaction records required for legal or financial compliance.</li>
      <li>Data required for fraud prevention and security purposes.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Retention Period</h2>

    <p>
      All deletable data will be permanently removed within
      <strong>7–30 days</strong> after receiving and verifying your request.
    </p>

    <h2>Questions?</h2>

    <p>
      Contact us at
      <a href="mailto:support.improvise@gmail.com">support.improvise@gmail.com</a>.
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
      © 2026 IMPROVISE. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
